title: Did my phone settings somehow get changed?
content:
I have restarted my phone several times and uninstalled updates to Chrome. I recently updated to Android 11.
I still can't search for GIFs within Messages, and while I can get to websites, the websites don't have proper functionality (I am unable to access information within them by clicking on links embedded within websites).
The ability to take a screenshot is also gone now.
I am also unable to download podcasts (using Castbox app).
Issue just started a couple of hours ago.
